snippet.title: Ascenders: Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a first look at the world in Ascenders, an upcoming sci-fantasy action adventure RPG from crypto-native developer Legendary Foundry Games. Ascenders is an open world experience with a fully decentralized, player driven economy powered by Avalanche blockchain.

Scheduled for release in Q4 2023.
